      ],
      "notes": "<p>A Bulb Digimon with a big flower blooming on its head. Yokomon moves by deftly manipulating its root-like tentacles, and is able to float softly through the air, albeit for short distances. A curious creature, its restless movements are delightful to behold. Yokomon tend to live in groups—from dozens to hundreds.</p>"
